HEADWORD: Stock-still
<hw>Stock"-still`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[CF. G.
<ets>stock-still</ets>.]</ety> <def>Still as a stock, or fixed post;
perfectly still.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>His whole work stands <qex>stock-still</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Sterne.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stockwork</ent>⟦br⟧
